name: Integrated Preamplifier
details:
Great clean preamp / Line driver and EQA very high input impedance, extreme low noise and distortion levels, powerful tone controls and built-in line driving capabilities makes TC Preamp a non-compromising preamplifier suited to many applications on stage and in the studio.
It can use either a 9-volt battery or an external power supply up to 32 Volts DC, which increase the headroom.
